1
00:00:26,420 --> 00:00:28,660
Help!

2
00:00:41,920 --> 00:00:43,160
Did you see it all

3
00:00:43,800 --> 00:00:45,800
with your own eyes?

4
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:47,040
I saw it myself.

5
00:00:47,520 --> 00:00:48,920
It's the truth.

6
00:00:49,270 --> 00:00:50,360
If this happened last night,

7
00:00:50,488 --> 00:00:52,760
why did you only report it
to the Bureau this morning?

8
00:00:53,320 --> 00:00:54,480
I...

9
00:00:54,480 --> 00:00:56,160
I was terrified!

10
00:00:56,720 --> 00:00:58,800
Red-Faced Guardian's curse
is still going on,

11
00:00:59,240 --> 00:01:01,400
so I had to hide until daybreak

12
00:01:02,400 --> 00:01:04,120
before I dared to come out.

13
00:01:05,960 --> 00:01:07,280
The body has multiple fractures.

14
00:01:07,800 --> 00:01:09,240
Severe bleeding from both eyes.

15
00:01:10,320 --> 00:01:11,880
Subcutaneous bruising.

16
00:01:15,680 --> 00:01:17,560
We're doomed.

17
00:01:18,120 --> 00:01:19,760
I've been cursed!

18
00:01:19,760 --> 00:01:21,520
I...

19
00:01:21,520 --> 00:01:22,770
I'm just as doomed!

20
00:01:24,330 --> 00:01:25,920
None of us is going to escape this.

21
00:01:27,560 --> 00:01:28,200
Zhuang...

22
00:01:28,200 --> 00:01:29,400
Zhuang Luobai...

23
00:01:29,520 --> 00:01:30,520
It was Zhuang Luobai!

24
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:32,560
He's the one who brought

25
00:01:32,560 --> 00:01:34,480
the Red-Faced Guardian's curse!

26
00:01:49,940 --> 00:01:56,460
=The Tang Mist S1=

27
00:03:15,100 --> 00:03:17,100
=Episode 8=

28
00:03:17,880 --> 00:03:18,680
Master,

29
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:21,320
have you heard?

30
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:26,480
Gu Pan'er's mother also suffered

31
00:03:27,060 --> 00:03:28,640
a curse from the Red-Faced Guardian.

32
00:03:30,200 --> 00:03:31,120
The Red-Faced Guardian

33
00:03:32,080 --> 00:03:33,360
protects the people.

34
00:03:34,440 --> 00:03:35,720
Where would a curse come from?

35
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:39,480
But Gu Pan'er broke the rules.

36
00:03:40,155 --> 00:03:41,160
Focus on your dancing.

37
00:03:41,511 --> 00:03:42,933
Don't worry about anything else.

38
00:03:48,920 --> 00:03:50,120
How can I not?

39
00:03:50,480 --> 00:03:51,880
You care about her so much.

40
00:03:52,200 --> 00:03:53,360
Ever since she married,

41
00:03:53,822 --> 00:03:55,377
you've become a different person.

42
00:03:56,320 --> 00:03:57,680
You constantly berate and beat me,

43
00:03:57,760 --> 00:03:59,800
taking your anger out on me.

44
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:03,000
Isn't all of this

45
00:04:03,880 --> 00:04:04,880
because of her?

46
00:04:10,490 --> 00:04:11,630
Is that

47
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:14,560
how you see me?

48
00:04:22,760 --> 00:04:23,840
Isn't it?

49
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:25,280
I've poured my heart

50
00:04:25,280 --> 00:04:26,480
into this dancing,

51
00:04:26,700 --> 00:04:28,288
yet it's never good enough for you.

52
00:04:30,840 --> 00:04:32,520
You refuse to give me any recognition,

53
00:04:32,960 --> 00:04:34,480
but the Troupe Master values me.

54
00:04:38,170 --> 00:04:39,511
So he's replacing you with me

55
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:41,720
for the Winter Festival.

56
00:04:49,160 --> 00:04:49,960
Master,

57
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:52,360
you've taken me in for ten years.

58
00:04:52,790 --> 00:04:54,890
The very bricks
on these floors have witnessed

59
00:04:55,410 --> 00:04:56,990
all the sweat and tears we've shed.

60
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:59,910
Gu Pan'er was always an outsider.

61
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:01,320
If she died, who cares?

62
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:03,560
It's good that it ended your obsession.

63
00:05:13,070 --> 00:05:13,980
Look at you.

64
00:05:15,840 --> 00:05:18,040
Ten years of heart and soul,

65
00:05:18,520 --> 00:05:20,680
and I've raised someone so cold-blooded.

66
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:26,080
You're right to scold me, Master.

67
00:05:27,320 --> 00:05:29,000
But this coldness is only for outsiders.

68
00:05:31,080 --> 00:05:32,200
When it comes to Nuo opera,

69
00:05:32,580 --> 00:05:33,870
I am completely dedicated.

70
00:05:34,880 --> 00:05:35,800
A Nuo performer

71
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:37,555
uses a righteous heart
to drive away evil.

72
00:05:37,822 --> 00:05:39,400
But yours is clouded by selfishness.

73
00:05:39,400 --> 00:05:40,690
The divine path is closed to you.

74
00:05:41,200 --> 00:05:42,280
Reflect on this yourself.

75
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:51,840
Get out.

76
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:57,320
I can't be your master anymore.

77
00:05:58,360 --> 00:06:00,040
I, Zhuang Luobai, have failed you.

78
00:06:09,733 --> 00:06:11,080
The hand that wields that iron rod

79
00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:12,200
has quite the talent.

80
00:06:14,440 --> 00:06:15,800
Listen more, learn more,

81
00:06:16,360 --> 00:06:17,200
and talk less.

82
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:24,280
This brush is already fraying.

83
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:31,320
I happen to have a good one here.

84
00:06:34,770 --> 00:06:36,320
You're just barely worthy of it.

85
00:06:37,320 --> 00:06:38,120
Take it.

86
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:54,920
Di.

87
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:56,790
Di!

88
00:06:56,880 --> 00:06:58,680
Gu Qi lied to us.

89
00:06:58,960 --> 00:06:59,600
Oh?

90
00:06:59,760 --> 00:07:01,440
Gu Pan'er wasn't without friends.

91
00:07:01,490 --> 00:07:02,960
She had a close confidante

92
00:07:02,960 --> 00:07:03,890
named Dong Ling.

93
00:07:03,950 --> 00:07:05,000
This lady looks...

94
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:06,000
Hold on, Duan.

95
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:07,840
I just dipped the brush in ink.

96
00:07:07,960 --> 00:07:08,560
Go on.

97
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:10,480
She's taller than the average woman.

98
00:07:10,500 --> 00:07:11,733
- Taller than you?
- Thin...

99
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,930
Thin lips, phoenix eyes.

100
00:07:17,990 --> 00:07:18,920
She rarely smiles,

101
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:20,960
but she seems like a kind soul.

102
00:07:20,960 --> 00:07:21,800
Draw!

103
00:07:28,880 --> 00:07:30,080
Raise the eyebrows a bit!

104
00:07:34,360 --> 00:07:35,920
Make the cheekbones more prominent!

105
00:07:44,540 --> 00:07:46,280
That looks just like their description.

106
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:47,760
Di.

107
00:07:49,520 --> 00:07:50,280
Di!

108
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:58,960
(I've seen her before.)

109
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:03,000
(The Nuo opera is starting!)

110
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:04,960
(Look, it's starting!)

111
00:08:04,960 --> 00:08:07,040
(Let's go to see Master Zhuang Luobai!)

112
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:11,300
Is this show still going on or what?

113
00:08:11,520 --> 00:08:12,360
Who is this?

114
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:13,910
We came to see Zhuang Luobai!

115
00:08:14,240 --> 00:08:15,880
We want to see Zhuang Luobai!

116
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:23,600
(Dong Ling...)

117
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:46,280
(Dong Ling)
Sirs, my mother has just passed.

118
00:08:46,280 --> 00:08:47,240
It's a mess inside.

119
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:48,120
We should talk here.

120
00:08:48,520 --> 00:08:49,640
Is that alright?

121
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:53,680
Do you know Gu Pan'er?

122
00:08:56,680 --> 00:08:58,160
She was murdered

123
00:08:58,240 --> 00:09:00,240
and left backstage at the theater.

124
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:04,140
When was the last time you saw her?

125
00:09:09,160 --> 00:09:10,360
Three days ago.

126
00:09:11,280 --> 00:09:13,640
She was with you the day she died.

127
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:15,440
Where did you go?

128
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:16,280
What did you do?

129
00:09:16,400 --> 00:09:17,520
When did you part ways?

130
00:09:21,160 --> 00:09:23,320
It was the day of my mother's funeral.

131
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:24,920
Pan'er...

132
00:09:25,880 --> 00:09:27,200
Pan'er came to pay her respects.

133
00:09:29,040 --> 00:09:30,280
She went home in the afternoon.

134
00:09:32,600 --> 00:09:34,800
Was there anything wrong
with her that day?

135
00:09:37,280 --> 00:09:38,080
No.

136
00:09:40,760 --> 00:09:42,360
Do you know

137
00:09:42,360 --> 00:09:44,440
who she was close to

138
00:09:44,560 --> 00:09:45,720
before she died?

139
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:51,320
You want to ask about

140
00:09:52,280 --> 00:09:53,960
her and Zhuang Luobai, right?

141
00:09:58,240 --> 00:09:59,760
There was nothing between them.

142
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:02,200
Why are you so sure?

143
00:10:03,177 --> 00:10:04,800
I've known Pan'er
since we were children.

144
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:05,800
We grew up together.

145
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:07,560
I know her character.

146
00:10:09,280 --> 00:10:10,040
Besides,

147
00:10:11,180 --> 00:10:12,110
she and Zhuang Luobai

148
00:10:12,180 --> 00:10:13,480
had known each other a year ago.

149
00:10:14,760 --> 00:10:15,911
If they really had an affair,

150
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:19,240
why would she have
married Hou Guangming?

151
00:10:22,280 --> 00:10:23,440
Didn't she marry Hou Guangming

152
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:24,860
for his money?

153
00:10:29,830 --> 00:10:30,900
She did it for me.

154
00:10:32,880 --> 00:10:34,080
For my mother's medical bills.

155
00:10:35,040 --> 00:10:36,340
That's why she agreed

156
00:10:36,422 --> 00:10:38,422
to let her father sell her
to Hou Guangming.

157
00:10:39,880 --> 00:10:41,360
Do you know Hou Guangming?

158
00:10:42,880 --> 00:10:43,680
No.

159
00:10:44,880 --> 00:10:45,920
But I asked around.

160
00:10:46,520 --> 00:10:47,240
They say

161
00:10:47,640 --> 00:10:48,840
he's an old scholar.

162
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:50,280
Kind,

163
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:51,311
well-read and cultured,

164
00:10:51,711 --> 00:10:53,000
and he treats Pan'er well.

165
00:10:54,840 --> 00:10:56,600
So their marriage

166
00:10:56,600 --> 00:10:57,740
must have been a happy one?

167
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:01,360
She never talked about it.

168
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:03,200
Whenever I asked,

169
00:11:03,760 --> 00:11:04,800
she'd say things were fine.

170
00:11:06,200 --> 00:11:07,200
But I knew.

171
00:11:08,880 --> 00:11:10,440
Married to a man she didn't love

172
00:11:12,520 --> 00:11:13,800
wouldn't make her happy.

173
00:11:15,640 --> 00:11:16,820
I could see it

174
00:11:16,850 --> 00:11:17,720
in her eyes.

175
00:11:18,630 --> 00:11:20,760
So, was Pan'er in love
with someone else?

176
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:27,560
Why are you asking?

177
00:11:28,080 --> 00:11:29,640
Do you suspect Hou Guangming killed her?

178
00:11:31,520 --> 00:11:32,720
I'm still investigating.

179
00:11:34,080 --> 00:11:36,560
You went to the theater the other day.

180
00:11:39,200 --> 00:11:40,560
Who were you meeting there?

181
00:11:41,680 --> 00:11:42,280
No one.

182
00:11:42,280 --> 00:11:43,355
Just watching the show.

183
00:11:44,040 --> 00:11:44,680
Sir!

184
00:11:45,640 --> 00:11:46,200
Sir!

185
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:47,760
Hou Guangming is
at the Bureau to see you.

186
00:11:47,770 --> 00:11:48,720
He's found evidence.

187
00:11:49,320 --> 00:11:50,680
My apologies for the interruption.

188
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:12,920
Sir,

189
00:12:13,880 --> 00:12:15,960
while I was going through
Pan'er's belongings,

190
00:12:17,240 --> 00:12:18,600
I suddenly remembered this.

191
00:12:31,590 --> 00:12:32,960
Are you suggesting

192
00:12:33,300 --> 00:12:35,140
this belongs to Zhuang Luobai?

193
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:36,440
It certainly does.

194
00:12:39,920 --> 00:12:41,400
Why are you so sure?

195
00:12:45,280 --> 00:12:47,000
I didn't want to air our dirty laundry,

196
00:12:48,120 --> 00:12:49,333
but to tell you the truth,

197
00:12:50,520 --> 00:12:51,560
a few days ago,

198
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:53,800
we had a huge fight

199
00:12:55,360 --> 00:12:56,840
over this robe.

200
00:13:07,280 --> 00:13:08,920
You're going to see Zhuang Luobai again?

201
00:13:15,120 --> 00:13:15,920
Pan'er,

202
00:13:17,360 --> 00:13:18,880
if you love Nuo opera so much,

203
00:13:19,270 --> 00:13:20,760
I'll hire a troupe to perform

204
00:13:21,020 --> 00:13:22,010
at our manor

205
00:13:22,120 --> 00:13:23,440
for three days and three nights.

206
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:24,400
How about that?

207
00:13:27,510 --> 00:13:28,440
You?

208
00:13:29,590 --> 00:13:31,200
You paid a fortune to buy me.

209
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:33,280
I've given you face in front of others,

210
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:35,920
but let's stop making
each other miserable here.

211
00:13:38,630 --> 00:13:39,470
Pan'er...

212
00:13:42,480 --> 00:13:44,480
I truly care about you.

213
00:13:47,680 --> 00:13:49,730
Money is indeed a good thing,

214
00:13:50,230 --> 00:13:51,960
but it only makes me greedier.

215
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:57,410
Look closely.

216
00:13:58,040 --> 00:14:00,640
The man in my heart is not like this.

217
00:14:07,320 --> 00:14:08,040
You can't leave!

218
00:14:08,040 --> 00:14:09,120
Don't go!

219
00:14:19,760 --> 00:14:20,560
Is this...

220
00:14:23,040 --> 00:14:24,600
You sewed this for him yourself?

221
00:14:26,160 --> 00:14:27,160
Give it back.

222
00:14:28,210 --> 00:14:29,120
But you...

223
00:14:31,040 --> 00:14:32,520
You've never even

224
00:14:32,920 --> 00:14:34,880
sewn a single stitch for me.

225
00:14:35,700 --> 00:14:36,780
Why are you crying?

226
00:14:39,040 --> 00:14:39,800
It's all my fault.

227
00:14:41,440 --> 00:14:43,240
Why did I have to argue with her?

228
00:14:44,640 --> 00:14:45,880
Now that I think about it,

229
00:14:46,870 --> 00:14:48,320
if she had just run off with someone,

230
00:14:48,320 --> 00:14:49,440
that would have been fine.

231
00:14:50,760 --> 00:14:53,100
Why did she have to die so brutally?

232
00:14:56,640 --> 00:14:58,200
From what I've observed,

233
00:14:58,600 --> 00:14:59,640
Zhuang Luobai

234
00:14:59,640 --> 00:15:02,080
only wears red
when performing Nuo opera.

235
00:15:02,840 --> 00:15:03,920
Normally,

236
00:15:03,920 --> 00:15:05,440
he only wears simple, plain robes.

237
00:15:07,440 --> 00:15:08,920
Then why would Gu Pan'er

238
00:15:09,480 --> 00:15:11,600
gift him a blue robe?

239
00:15:13,240 --> 00:15:14,040
Sir,

240
00:15:14,880 --> 00:15:15,760
we're at the Bureau,

241
00:15:16,200 --> 00:15:17,520
and I would never dare lie to you.

242
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:19,040
Relax.

243
00:15:20,720 --> 00:15:22,200
It's not that I don't believe you.

244
00:15:23,400 --> 00:15:24,240
Get up.

245
00:15:29,760 --> 00:15:30,600
Please.

246
00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:34,360
You must get justice

247
00:15:36,155 --> 00:15:37,360
for Pan'er and her mother.

248
00:15:48,360 --> 00:15:50,360
You suspect he's lying?

249
00:15:52,840 --> 00:15:53,640
Yes.

250
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:56,120
If the victim

251
00:15:56,120 --> 00:15:57,800
had an affair with Zhuang Luobai,

252
00:15:58,600 --> 00:15:59,920
he would be the prime suspect.

253
00:16:01,400 --> 00:16:03,960
But if what Dong Ling said is true,

254
00:16:04,080 --> 00:16:06,760
that there was no affair,

255
00:16:07,640 --> 00:16:08,640
then why would he

256
00:16:09,160 --> 00:16:12,240
be so desperate to frame Zhuang Luobai?

257
00:16:14,890 --> 00:16:15,760
Framing?

258
00:16:18,920 --> 00:16:20,920
But the footprints at the scene

259
00:16:20,920 --> 00:16:22,400
don't match his.

260
00:16:57,940 --> 00:16:59,920
Why is there an extra body here?

261
00:17:06,700 --> 00:17:07,820
(Preview of Next Episode)

262
00:17:17,000 --> 00:17:18,160
Father,

263
00:17:19,460 --> 00:17:21,480
Mother says it's time to come home

264
00:17:22,040 --> 00:17:23,440
for dinner.

265
00:17:40,590 --> 00:17:42,170
♪Night covers the long streets♪

266
00:17:43,250 --> 00:17:44,960
♪The city remains silent♪

267
00:17:46,350 --> 00:17:47,940
♪Wind turns the old pages♪

268
00:17:48,200 --> 00:17:50,440
♪Words still left unspoken♪

269
00:17:51,840 --> 00:17:53,480
♪Bloodstains still hold their warmth♪

270
00:17:54,610 --> 00:17:57,080
♪Lamplight slowly tilts aside♪

271
00:17:57,700 --> 00:17:59,180
♪Who hides in the shadows♪

272
00:17:59,180 --> 00:18:02,320
♪Still circling around the truth?♪

273
00:18:02,940 --> 00:18:04,860
♪Love is born from desire♪

274
00:18:05,550 --> 00:18:07,680
♪Hatred rises out of greed♪

275
00:18:08,820 --> 00:18:10,480
♪One thought becomes a snare♪

276
00:18:10,480 --> 00:18:13,780
♪A lifetime trapped within♪

277
00:18:15,230 --> 00:18:16,550
♪Someone once warned me♪

278
00:18:16,550 --> 00:18:18,070
♪To stop upon this shore♪

279
00:18:18,070 --> 00:18:19,390
♪But sunlight burns too fiercely♪

280
00:18:19,390 --> 00:18:20,880
♪Fragile eyes break too easily♪

281
00:18:20,880 --> 00:18:22,000
♪If one thought retreats♪

282
00:18:22,000 --> 00:18:23,300
♪Then all things rest in peace♪

283
00:18:23,300 --> 00:18:24,640
♪But in this world♪

284
00:18:24,640 --> 00:18:27,040
♪Who will make the final judgment?♪

285
00:18:28,870 --> 00:18:31,680
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

286
00:18:31,680 --> 00:18:33,150
♪Still I walk ahead♪

287
00:18:33,380 --> 00:18:34,600
♪Let it pierce through♪

288
00:18:34,600 --> 00:18:39,340
♪The illusions before my eyes♪

289
00:18:39,340 --> 00:18:41,580
♪Layer upon layer of deception♪

290
00:18:41,580 --> 00:18:42,980
♪Covering every heart♪

291
00:18:42,980 --> 00:18:44,170
♪How many people♪

292
00:18:44,430 --> 00:18:45,800
♪Weave their own cocoon♪

293
00:18:45,800 --> 00:18:48,010
♪Yet call it♪

294
00:18:48,210 --> 00:18:49,550
♪Fate?♪

295
00:18:49,910 --> 00:18:51,090
♪Life and death♪

296
00:18:51,090 --> 00:18:52,350
♪Balanced on a single line♪

297
00:18:52,700 --> 00:18:53,870
♪Light and shadow♪

298
00:18:53,870 --> 00:18:55,130
♪Hanging side by side♪

299
00:18:55,130 --> 00:18:56,610
♪Goodness is not absolute♪

300
00:18:56,610 --> 00:18:58,020
♪Nor is evil ever complete♪

301
00:18:58,020 --> 00:18:59,560
♪In the end, it is only♪

302
00:18:59,560 --> 00:19:00,940
♪A single misguided thought♪

303
00:19:00,940 --> 00:19:02,500
♪If unveiling the truth♪

304
00:19:02,500 --> 00:19:03,840
♪Requires abandoning tenderness♪

305
00:19:03,840 --> 00:19:05,010
♪Then this answer♪

306
00:19:05,010 --> 00:19:06,370
♪Can it still remain true?♪

307
00:19:06,370 --> 00:19:07,770
♪When love and law♪

308
00:19:07,770 --> 00:19:09,250
♪Stand against each other in silence♪

309
00:19:09,250 --> 00:19:10,650
♪Which figure before me♪

310
00:19:10,650 --> 00:19:17,850
♪Am I meant to believe?♪

311
00:19:17,850 --> 00:19:20,580
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

312
00:19:20,580 --> 00:19:22,170
♪Still I walk ahead♪

313
00:19:22,170 --> 00:19:23,410
♪Not for fame or glory♪

314
00:19:23,410 --> 00:19:28,280
♪Nor caring who wins or loses♪

315
00:19:28,280 --> 00:19:30,090
♪Human nature is clouded♪

316
00:19:30,090 --> 00:19:31,810
♪Yet still reflects the stars♪

317
00:19:31,810 --> 00:19:33,280
♪Though this world♪

318
00:19:33,280 --> 00:19:34,650
♪Is filled with mud and mire♪

319
00:19:34,650 --> 00:19:36,900
♪There is still a light♪

320
00:19:36,900 --> 00:19:39,860
♪Worth pursuing♪

321
00:19:39,860 --> 00:19:41,680
♪Every case has its ending♪

322
00:19:41,680 --> 00:19:42,940
♪But night does not always fade♪

323
00:19:43,210 --> 00:19:44,590
♪The wind stops, the pages close♪

324
00:19:44,590 --> 00:19:45,810
♪Yet hearts remain unsettled♪

325
00:19:46,080 --> 00:19:47,160
♪If justice stands♪

326
00:19:47,160 --> 00:19:48,410
♪Without mercy beside it♪

327
00:19:48,410 --> 00:19:50,210
♪Then how is it♪

328
00:19:50,210 --> 00:19:59,770
♪Any different from a blade?♪

329
00:19:59,770 --> 00:20:02,960
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

330
00:20:02,960 --> 00:20:04,440
♪Still I walk ahead♪

331
00:20:04,440 --> 00:20:05,830
♪Even if the world♪

332
00:20:05,830 --> 00:20:10,560
♪Refuses to answer♪

333
00:20:10,560 --> 00:20:12,520
♪When every hidden truth♪

334
00:20:12,520 --> 00:20:14,230
♪Finally reveals itself♪

335
00:20:14,230 --> 00:20:15,590
♪I only wish♪

336
00:20:15,590 --> 00:20:17,070
♪To hold on♪

337
00:20:17,070 --> 00:20:21,810
♪Within the darkness♪

338
00:20:21,810 --> 00:20:23,810
♪To the heart♪

